Dependencies
libbde requires:
* libcrypto (OpenSSL) or Windows Crypto API from the Windows Platform SDK
  (optional but recommended)

bdemount requires:
* libfuse
  (optional but recommended)


Solaris
To build libbde on Solaris make sure that /usr/ccs/bin and /usr/swf/bin are defined in the PATH environment variable


Also see:
* README.dll
* README.macosx
* README.mingw
* README.static

